data.description: Better than new! This home features fresh paint, upgrades, and classy touches in a great location. You'll love how bright this home feels with the oversized windows. High ceilings on both levels add to the open feel. The kitchen features a huge quartz island and walk-in pantry plus an additional desk area. Upstairs you will find the bedrooms plus a bonus loft that would be perfect as an office or flex space. Master has a large vanity with double sinks and the shower has just been updated. All of this is on a corner lot in a neighborhood with a pool in the Brookwood school district. Very conveniently located with easy access to Ronald Reagan PKWY, I-85, or Hwy 78.  Brand new irrigation system. Priced to sell quickly!
